OL,3,CFalklands becomes political football
OL,4,Cahead of Argentina and England grudge
OL,5,Cmatch
OL,7,FArgentinian players and politicians
OL,8,Fhave put the Falkland Islands dispute
OL,9,Fcentre stage as the decades-old
OL,10,Frivalry with England heats up again
OL,11,Fahead of a crunch World Cup semi-final
OL,12,Fon Wednesday.
OL,14,FFollowing their victory over
OL,15,FSwitzerland in the quarter-finals over
OL,16,Fthe weekend, the South American
OL,17,Ffootball team was filmed singing a
OL,18,Fsong about defeating the Three Lions
OL,19,F"for the Malvinas" - the Spanish name
OL,20,Ffor the British Overseas Territory.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
