OL,3,CFalklands becomes political football
OL,4,Cahead of Argentina and England grudge
OL,5,Cmatch
OL,7,FArgentina forward Jose Manuel Lopez
OL,8,Flater acknowledged: "Obviously,
OL,9,Foutside the four lines of the pitch,
OL,10,Fit's a matchup that has a lot of
OL,11,Fhistory, a lot of pain, and a lot
OL,12,Fbehind it.
OL,14,F"It's a World Cup semi-final, a game
OL,15,Fthat I think all of my teammates have
OL,16,Fdreamed of playing since we first
OL,17,Fstarted kicking a ball. We don't need
OL,18,Fany more motivation than that."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
