OL,3,CFalklands becomes political football
OL,4,Cahead of Argentina and England grudge
OL,5,Cmatch
OL,7,FOn Monday, Argentine Foreign Minister
OL,8,FPablo Quirno also reasserted claims to
OL,9,Fthe islands, which have been under
OL,10,FBritish rule since 1833.
OL,12,FArgentina has long claimed sovereignty
OL,13,Fover the Falklands and invaded them in
OL,14,F1982 before being defeated in a short
OL,15,Fbut bloody 10-week war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
