OL,3,CFalklands becomes political football
OL,4,Cahead of Argentina and England grudge
OL,5,Cmatch
OL,7,FFour years later, Diego Maradona's
OL,8,Finfamous 1986 "Hand of God" goal
OL,9,Feliminated England, a controversy that
OL,10,Fhas only added to the hostility
OL,11,Fbetween Three Lions and La Albiceleste
OL,12,Ffans.
OL,14,FAfter illegally punching the ball into
OL,15,Fthe net, Maradona called the 2-1
OL,16,Fquarter-final victory "symbolic
OL,17,Frevenge" over the United Kingdom.
OL,26,@pD@OOUpD@[O]xD@WOUyD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
