OL,3,CFalklands becomes political football
OL,4,Cahead of Argentina and England grudge
OL,5,Cmatch
OL,7,FQuirno, a minister in the government
OL,8,Fof Trump's "favourite president,"
OL,9,FJavier Milei, demanded Britain enter
OL,10,Ftalks to hand over the Falklands.
OL,12,FHe said: "Time does not transform an
OL,13,Fillegitimate occupation into
OL,14,Fsovereignty. Nor will it divide the
OL,15,Fterritorial unity of the Argentine
OL,16,FRepublic
OL,18,F"Our claim will not be relinquished,
OL,19,Fresigned, or abandoned.
OL,26,@tD@JOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
