OL,3,CFalklands becomes political football
OL,4,Cahead of Argentina and England grudge
OL,5,Cmatch
OL,7,FIn a lengthy essay for the leading
OL,8,Fconservative paper La Nacion, he
OL,9,Fargued a 2013 referendum held on the
OL,10,Farchipelago, in which 99.8 per cent of
OL,11,Fislanders chose to remain British, was
OL,12,Fillegitimate because they were
OL,13,F"artificially implanted by the
OL,14,Foccupying power".
OL,16,FArgentina views the vote as a sham.
OL,26,@pD@[rw
