OL,3,CFalklands becomes political football
OL,4,Cahead of Argentina and England grudge
OL,5,Cmatch
OL,7,FIn April, an internal Pentagon email
OL,8,Fset out options for President Donald
OL,9,FTrump's administration to punish Nato
OL,10,Fallies - including Sir Keir Starmer -
OL,11,Fwho refused to join US-Israeli strikes
OL,12,Fon Iran.
OL,14,FAmong the suggestions was to review
OL,15,FAmerica's position on "imperial
OL,16,Fpossessions" such as the South
OL,17,FAtlantic territory.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
