OL,4,Cahead of Argentina and England grudge
OL,5,Cmatch
OL,7,FOn Monday, Starmer's official
OL,8,Fspokesman said: "I think the prime
OL,9,Fminister's view is that football
OL,10,Fshould be about a game and about
OL,11,Fbringing people together. That's what
OL,12,Ffans want to see."
OL,14,FEngland booked a semi-final date with
OL,15,FArgentina at Atlanta's Mercedes-Benz
OL,16,FStadium with a hard-fought extra-time
OL,17,Fwin over Norway in Saturday's quarter-
OL,18,Ffinal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
