OL,7,FThe meeting will be the first time
OL,8,FLionel Messi has played against the
OL,9,FThree Lions, but his country's sixth
OL,10,FWorld Cup meeting with England.
OL,12,FOne of England and Argentina's most
OL,13,Fmemorable clashes was the 1986 quarter-
OL,14,Ffinal at the Azteca Stadium, Mexico
OL,15,FCity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
