OL,3,CFalklands becomes political football
OL,4,Cahead of Argentina and England grudge
OL,5,Cmatch
OL,7,FMaradona's "Hand of God" remains
OL,8,Findelibly etched in the minds of all
OL,9,Fwho witnessed it as the diminutive
OL,10,Fmidfielder outjumped goalkeeper Peter
OL,11,FShilton with the aid of a raised arm
OL,12,Fto knock the ball into the net.
OL,14,FThe rivalry dates back to July 1966 -
OL,15,FEnglish football's greatest summer -
OL,16,Fwhen Sir Alf Ramsey's team lifted the
OL,17,FWorld Cup.
OL,26,@oD@LOUoD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
