OL,3,CFalklands becomes political football
OL,4,Cahead of Argentina and England grudge
OL,5,Cmatch
OL,7,FMeanwhile, despite Wednesday's fixture
OL,8,Fbeing rich in history, central
OL,9,Fmidfielder Reece James said England
OL,10,Fwill be able to cope with the occasion.
OL,12,FHe told reporters: "The higher stakes
OL,13,Fthe game is, the more pressure. We've
OL,14,Fbeen doing it for years, the
OL,15,Ffundamentals are the same, but the
OL,16,Fprize is slightly different.
OL,18,F"We're in a bubble, trying to complete
OL,19,Four mission. It's hard to see the
OL,20,Foutside. We're happy we're making
OL,21,Feveryone at home proud.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
